====================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                |NAME|EST. ROWS|COST   |
----------------------------------------------------
|0 |SUBPLAN SCAN            |rw  |10900    |1635708|
|1 | RECURSIVE UNION ALL    |    |10900    |1634203|
|2 |  NESTED-LOOP JOIN      |    |7841     |1616836|
|3 |   EXCHANGE IN DISTR    |    |2000     |1135   |
|4 |    EXCHANGE OUT DISTR  |    |2000     |543    |
|5 |     TABLE SCAN         |e   |2000     |543    |
|6 |   MATERIAL             |    |2000     |2557   |
|7 |    EXCHANGE IN DISTR   |    |2000     |903    |
|8 |     EXCHANGE OUT DISTR |    |2000     |477    |
|9 |      TABLE SCAN        |d   |2000     |477    |
|10|  HASH JOIN             |    |3059     |12627  |
|11|   MATERIAL             |    |2000     |1638   |
|12|    EXCHANGE IN DISTR   |    |2000     |903    |
|13|     EXCHANGE OUT DISTR |    |2000     |477    |
|14|      TABLE SCAN        |d   |2000     |477    |
|15|   HASH JOIN            |    |781      |5113   |
|16|    TABLE SCAN          |r   |1        |1      |
|17|    MATERIAL            |    |2000     |1870   |
|18|     EXCHANGE IN DISTR  |    |2000     |1135   |
|19|      EXCHANGE OUT DISTR|    |2000     |543    |
|20|       TABLE SCAN       |e   |2000     |543    |
====================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([rw.ename], [rw.empno], [rw.mgr]), filter(nil), 
      access([rw.ename], [rw.empno], [rw.mgr])
  1 - output([UNION(e.ENAME, e.ENAME)], [UNION(e.MGR, e.MGR)], [UNION(e.EMPno, e.EMPno)]), filter(nil)
  2 - output([e.ENAME], [e.MGR], [e.EMPno]), filter(nil), 
      conds([e.SAL = d.SAL]), nl_params_(nil)
