|10|   HASH JOIN                  |    |10       |48776|
|11|    NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN|    |3383     |3015 |
|12|     TABLE SCAN               |r   |1        |1    |
|13|     MATERIAL                 |    |17       |90   |
|14|      TABLE SCAN              |n   |17       |40   |
