|4 |    EXCHANGE OUT DISTR  |    |21       |38  |
|5 |     TABLE SCAN         |e   |21       |38  |
|6 |   MATERIAL             |    |21       |46  |
|7 |    EXCHANGE IN DISTR   |    |21       |40  |
|8 |     EXCHANGE OUT DISTR |    |21       |38  |
|9 |      TABLE SCAN        |d   |21       |38  |
