|11|   MATERIAL             |    |21       |47  |
|12|    EXCHANGE IN DISTR   |    |21       |40  |
|13|     EXCHANGE OUT DISTR |    |21       |38  |
|14|      TABLE SCAN        |d   |21       |38  |
|15|   HASH JOIN            |    |9        |172 |
|16|    MATERIAL            |    |21       |52  |
|17|     EXCHANGE IN DISTR  |    |21       |44  |
|18|      EXCHANGE OUT DISTR|    |21       |38  |
|19|       TABLE SCAN       |e   |21       |38  |
|20|    TABLE SCAN          |r   |1        |1   |
=================================================

